svg.title: Mozilla Firefox logo 2013
svg.description: Firefox logo used since June 2013 (version 23.0 Beta). Note that the logo is a trademark, and the trademark rights are neither liberated nor otherwise granted to you. Also, only the logo files distributed with the official Firefox releases were released under the Mozilla tri-license. As of 2012, logos of Firefox before version 3.5 are not under any free license. In July 2015, Firefox branding guidelines say: “The logo files containing our trademarks are available under the following copyright licenses: vector logo files under CC-BY 3.0 or later; bitmap logo files under MPL 2.”
